### Variables de entorno
@host = http://localhost:8080/api/invoices
@authToken = Bearer tu_token_aqui
@invoiceId = id_de_tu_factura_aqui
@orderId = id_de_tu_orden_aqui

### ============================================
### FLUJO ONLINE COMPLETO
### ============================================

### 1️⃣ CLIENTE CREA ORDEN ONLINE
### Primero se crea la orden en /api/orders con channel=ONLINE
### POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
### {
###   "channel": "ONLINE",
###   "customerId": 1,
###   "items": [...]
### }
### Respuesta: "order-uuid-123"

### 2️⃣ SISTEMA CREA FACTURA AUTOMÁTICAMENTE
### Se crea automáticamente cuando KITCHEN marca la orden como COMPLETED
### PUT http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{orderId}
### {
###   "status": "COMPLETED"
### }

### 3️⃣ CLIENTE PAGA CON WOMPI
POST {{host}}/{{invoiceId}}/pay-online
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceId": "INV-20260409-ABC123",
  "wompiToken": "eJydUsFuwjAM_ZWLT",
  "customerEmail": "cliente@example.com",
  "customerPhone": "+573001234567",
  "notes": "Pago exitoso con Wompi"
}

### Respuesta (200 OK):
### {
###   "data": {
###     "id": "INV-20260409-ABC123",
###     "orderId": "order-uuid-123",
###     "status": "PAID",
###     "subtotal": 50000.0,
###     "tax": 4000.0,
###     "total": 54000.0,
###     "paidAt": "2026-04-09T16:30:00"
###   },
###   "error": false
### }

### ============================================
### FLUJO PRESENCIAL COMPLETO
### ============================================

### 1️⃣ MESERO CREA ORDEN PRESENCIAL
### POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
### {
###   "channel": "PRESENCIAL",
###   "waiterId": 5,
###   "tableNumber": "A1",
###   "items": [...]
### }
### Respuesta: "order-uuid-456"

### 2️⃣ KITCHEN PREPARA INMEDIATAMENTE (SIN ESPERAR PAGO)
### PUT http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{orderId}
### {
###   "status": "COMPLETED"
### }
### La orden se marca como COMPLETED y se crea factura automáticamente

### 3️⃣ CLIENTE PAGA EN EFECTIVO
POST {{host}}/{{invoiceId}}/pay-presential
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceId": "INV-20260409-DEF456",
  "paymentMethod": "CASH",
  "reference": null,
  "notes": "Pagó en efectivo"
}

### Respuesta (200 OK):
### {
###   "data": {
###     "id": "INV-20260409-DEF456",
###     "status": "PAID",
###     "total": 25000.0,
###     "paidAt": "2026-04-09T17:15:00"
###   },
###   "error": false
### }

### ============================================
### 3️⃣ ALTERNATIVA: CLIENTE PAGA POR TRANSFERENCIA
### ============================================
POST {{host}}/{{invoiceId}}/pay-presential
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceId": "INV-20260409-DEF456",
  "paymentMethod": "TRANSFER",
  "reference": "TRF-2026-0001",
  "notes": "Transferencia bancaria confirmada"
}

### ============================================
### 3️⃣ ALTERNATIVA: CLIENTE PAGA CON TARJETA FÍSICA
### ============================================
POST {{host}}/{{invoiceId}}/pay-presential
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceId": "INV-20260409-DEF456",
  "paymentMethod": "CARD",
  "reference": "TRX-POS-123456",
  "notes": "Pagó con tarjeta física en POS"
}

### ============================================
### CONSULTAS
### ============================================

### Obtener detalle de factura
GET {{host}}/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Obtener todas las facturas (solo ADMIN)
GET {{host}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### CANCELAR FACTURA (si no está pagada)
### ============================================
DELETE {{host}}/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### MÉTODOS DE PAGO PERMITIDOS
### ============================================
###
### ONLINE (Wompi):
###  - WOMPI: Pasarela de pagos
###
### PRESENCIAL:
###  - CASH: Efectivo
###  - CARD: Tarjeta física (POS/Datafono)
###  - TRANSFER: Transferencia bancaria
###  - CHECK: Cheque
###
### ============================================
### ESTADOS DE FACTURA
### ============================================
###
###  - PENDING: Factura creada, esperando pago
###  - PAID: Pagada completamente
###  - CANCELLED: Cancelada/Anulada
###
### ============================================

